KG name: Drug Data from the Health Insurance Fund of Macedonia
Description: Linked Open Drug Data from the Health Insurance Fund of the Republic of Macedonia. The dataset provides data about the referent (nominal) prices of drugs in Macedonia- along with the generic drug name- brand name- packaging- manufacturer- etc. The drugs from the dataset are linked among themselves with a "similar to" relation- and with an "owl:seeAlso" relation with corresponding drugs from the [DrugBank dataset](http://wifo5-03.informatik.uni-mannheim.de/drugbank/ "DrugBank"). Both relations are based on the drug ATC code.The drug data from the Fund is described using a custom HIFM ontology- along with relations from the DrugBank dataset. For more info on the dataset- please refer to [this paper](http://e-tnc.com/etnc/Portals/3/papers/loddhifm-ciit2013.pdf "LODD from the HIFM").
